//Purpose: jText Field List File for ts_store main event core columns (common)
//Related: type=ts_store

=== Fields ===
 1. #/# thread_id/Number/Not Null # originating thread (0-based)
 2. #/# per_thread_event_id/Number/Not Null # per-thread sequence
 3. #/# flags_raw/String # 0x... raw flags
 4. #/# category/String # event category/tag
 5. #/# payload/String # main payload text
 6. #/# timestamp_us/Number # microsecond timestamp
